Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-python, dh-sequence-python3, dh-sequence-sphinxdoc <!nodoc>, libjs-highlight.js <!nodoc>, python3-all, python3-click, python3-dotenv, python3-jsonschema, python3-pytest <!nocheck>, python3-requests, python3-setuptools, python3-sphinx <!nodoc>, python3-stac-validator, python3-yaml
Description: Linting and validation tool for STAC assets stac-check is both a CLI tool and Python library. It adds additional linting and validation to the stac-validator project. . The intent of this project is to provide a linting tool that also follows the official STAC Best Practices document.
Package-List: python-stac-check-doc deb doc optional arch=all python3-stac-check deb python optional arch=all stac-check deb utils optional arch=all
